{"tid":2186437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倪匡：「要毀滅一個大城市，不一定是天災，也可以是人禍...」","createTime":"2020-09-03T03:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T09:57:53.000Z","uid":143883,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2a36b38dc5c72ea956d9385fad2c59458c68f3","tid":2186437,"uid":143883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"「東方一個大城市會徹底毀滅，這些都是『氣數』，沒有方法可以挽回，天知地知你知我知這個大城市的名稱，也知道這個大城市在什麼時候毀滅。<br />\n<br />\n要毀滅一個大城市，不一定是天災，也可以是人禍，人禍不一定是戰爭，幾個人的幾句話，幾個人的愚昧無知的行動，可以令大城市徹底死亡。不必摧毀大城市的建築物，不必殺害大城市的任何一個居民，甚至在表面上看來，這個大城市和以前一樣，但只要令城市原來的優點消失，就可以令它毀滅死亡。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 倪匡《追龍》"},{"pid":"d62a8175d972212e760f00b3e679c69b2b42bd98","tid":2186437,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"幾個人係邊幾個？"},{"pid":"e8d1daa1960339b5c76330fe309fbce42974b757","tid":2186437,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62a8175d972212e760f00b3e679c69b2b42bd98","tid":2186437,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"幾個人係邊幾個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"天知地知你知我知"},{"pid":"d695daad3b343a2c074ab8b24137232c012da1f0","tid":2186437,"uid":143883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62a8175d972212e760f00b3e679c69b2b42bd98","tid":2186437,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"幾個人係邊幾個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"或者唔止幾個, 係幾班...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb5f5804623dade13f176aad08a5742c5d97962","tid":2186437,"uid":253039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"細個睇唔係好明 覺得好空泛<br />\n大個睇就知佢一早有設想過將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}